ping mechanism could eliminate two of the four backslashes - not sure it is worth the effort.", "url": "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/8484#discussion_r410137909", "createdAt": "2020-04-17T10:32:41Z", "author": {"login": "ppalaga"}, "path": "integration-tests/main/src/main/resources/application.properties", "diffHunk": "@@ -37,3 +37,5 @@ configproperties.message=Hello\n configproperties.other=1\n \n quarkus.swagger-ui.always-include=true\n+\n+quarkus.native.resources.includes = test-resources/.*\\\\\\\\.txt", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQxMDEyNDI5Ng=="}, "originalCommit": {"oid": "e8a9f3c25460e994459301e1924199a9e28cda52"}, "originalPosition": 5}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQxMTA2ODQzNA==", "bodyText": "Maybe globs are better, what do you think @gsmet ?", "url": "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/8484#discussion_r411068434", "createdAt": "2020-04-20T03:26:04Z", "author": {"login": "stuartwdouglas"}, "path": "integration-tests/main/src/main/resources/application.properties", "diffHunk": "@@ -37,3 +37,5 @@ configproperties.message=Hello\n configproperties.other=1\n \n quarkus.swagger-ui.always-include=true\n+\n+quarkus.native.resources.includes = test-resources/.*\\\\\\\\.txt", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQxMDEyNDI5Ng=="}, "originalCommit": {"oid": "e8a9f3c25460e994459301e1924199a9e28cda52"}, "originalPosition": 5}]}}]}}}, "rateLimit": {"limit": 5000, "remaining": 3678, "cost": 1, "resetAt": "2021-11-13T14:23:39Z"}}}